<div class="title">Don't Plan on Sleeping</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamine (Adderall)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Fed&Exact=1">Fed</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Fed. "Don't Plan on Sleeping: An Experience with Amphetamine (Adderall) (exp4603)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Dec 28, 2001. erowid.org/exp/4603</div>

